## 1. Project Overview & Objective

**Project Name:** Movie Ticket Booking Application (BookMyShow Clone)
**Tech Stack:** MERN Stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js)

**Objective:**
To build a modern, scalable, and highly interactive web application that allows users to seamlessly browse movies, select seats in real-time, order concessions, and securely pay for movie tickets. The platform also includes a robust Admin Dashboard for cinema management and a built-in QR Code Ticket Scanner for cinema staff.

